{
  "stem": "22734.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We just didn't believe-- we were completely reckless.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We felt nothing will happen to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We have a guardian angel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Nothing happened to us, as a matter of fact.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But if my mother would have known that-- I think she had an inkling-- but she-- she would have been desperate.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we met at all kinds of places.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was crazy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That was crazy what we did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I wouldn't do it today.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But it was fun.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "At least we had something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we-- we were so scared that we'll be separated.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That he'll go with a transport, and I'll go with another transport.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what are we going to do?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we'll never see each other again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were really-- that-- that drove us to desperation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it turned out fine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then while my father was in jail, we were called into this transport, which was a penalty transport.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First, they killed [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Heidrich. ?] That was, I described that in the book.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was-- that was an eerie situation because we were returning from a trip to the country without the Stars of David when this-- this whole announcement came.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was martial law, and if you didn't live through martial law in an occupied city, you don't know what-- what it is.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that night-- I mean, we parted, and we were very scared.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I ran home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that night, I slept in the kitchen and a guy came in with our neighbor, who was at that point German.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he-- he just scared the people who were living there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He didn't want anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he-- he just wanted to see our papers, and whether everybody who is in this house is accounted for, who is-- and whether we are supposed to be there.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
